			<h1 class="ctr">Welcome to Banstead Centre</h1>
			<p class="ctr">
			<a href="news.html">NEWS click for latest Centre news</a> 
			
			<p class="ctr">
			<span>We are waiting for the contract from Reigate &amp; Banstead 
			Council so that <br />
			Staywell can take over the Centre. See <a href="news.html">NEWS </a> for further information</span></p>
			<p class="ctr">
			The Banstead Centre is situated in The Horseshoe, 
		near the Library and the Clinic. <br />
			The building also houses the Citizens’ Advice Bureau and Age Concern. </p>
			<p class="ctr">
			The 
			<span>Reigate &amp; </span>Banstead Council Help Shop is now closed</p>
			<p class="ctr">
			It is open to members 10am to 4pm Monday to Friday</p>
			<p class="ctr">
			membership is open to persons 50 years and over</p>
			<p class="ctr">
			There are over 700 members </p>
			<p class="ctr">
			we have a Cafe for snacks and refreshments and a dining room for lunch for members</p>
			<p class="ctr">
			We provides a large numbers of activities for members</p>
			<p class="ctr">
			There is a Meeting Suite (ideal for 
		training/corporate meetings) and a smaller meeting room available for 
		<a href="hire/hire.html">hire </a>at any time.
		The whole centre or rooms within the Centre are also is available evenings and weekends 
		for hire i.e. training days, weddings, clubs, etc.<o:p></o:p></p>
		<p class="ctr">The Centre has a Hair Salon for ladies and gents hair</p>
			<p class="ctr">There is a Internet Cafe open 10 am to 3pm This 
			provides access to the internet and can 
			provide computer training if required</p>
			
			<p class="ctr">For a map of the centre's location <a href="images/MAP.pdf">m<span class="auto-style2">ap.pdf</span></a></p>
